title: Fully furnished Apartment 1Bed
posting_body: ['1 bedroom/ 1 bath fully furnished apartment Centrally located 1 block from Coral Gables in Miami, FL 33133 United States', 'This Contemporary apartment is inside a Fourplex property in a 1940’s neighborhood.', 'This unit is good for couples, solo adventures, and business travelers.', 'Cozy with all the basic necessities for a pleasant stay.', 'Very good location, centrally located 1 block from Coral Gables.', 'All properties are fully furnished and all-inclusive.', 'Nearby Attractions:', '1.5 miles to Coconut Grove, 5 miles to Brickell & Downtown Miami, and 3 miles Little Havana.', 'Near to everything in Miami, 33133 zip code.', 'It will take you little time to get anywhere, restaurants, markets, shopping, nightlife, attractions, airport, beaches…', 'Distances:', 'Metrorail Station (15 min walk)', '5 miles from the Miami International airport', '5 miles from the cruise port', 'Minutes away from US1 which connects to all major highways', '1/2 mile to Miracle Mile and everything Coral Gables has to offer.', 'Restaurants, Shops at Merrick Park, Miracle Mile, and shopping are all just blocks away!', 'Amenities:  None', 'Lease Terms', 'For the move in we require:', '- First Months Rent', "- Security Deposit (equal to the first month's rent)", '- Pet Fee (If applicable) $300 nonrefundable', '- Application fee', '- Cleaning Fee at check-out', 'For more pictures and info contact us:', 'CORPORATE HOUSING FOR RENT', 'Call now!', 'show contact info']
